{"tid":574262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解JR優美開始呢類人日日比人屌都仲咁鍾意上連登?","createTime":"2018-02-27T08:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T08:33:08.000Z","uid":58104,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ce15b27d1ff5730a86e80ba9ba69575cdf51c1","tid":574262,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去一個地方日撚日比人屌<br />\n仲要樂此不疲日日上<br />\n<br />\n人一般係想得到認同感既生物<br />\n係一個地方意見下下同主流相反<br />\n仲要格格不入<br />\n仲賴死唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係個乜撚野JR(反本土，反港獨)<br />\n連登/高登好明顯係本土/港獨思想發源地啦<br />\n反你老母咩，反港獨反本土你就去yahoo新聞評論/香討圍爐取暖啦屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n除左收左錢(五毫子)<br />\n或者天生被虐狂唔屌唔鬆化<br />\n我都諗唔到有咩解釋到<br />\n<br />\n我屌你班死五毛死仆街冚家剷屌你老母"},{"pid":"05e1563d52c21d55e8d678c8d352cca3ab4f2602","tid":574262,"uid":108606,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"因為比人屌係份人工包埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba57d35b3258b697a3ba9b259a0c264c1376327","tid":574262,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢地咁勤力，似自乾五多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b893cf9701bf37d36ff0f7e52e1cbff1ce1c291","tid":574262,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8096157aecd241f37f1d350da0553b502cd54f98","tid":574262,"uid":58104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7b893cf9701bf37d36ff0f7e52e1cbff1ce1c291","tid":574262,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"你都叫女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死肥西"},{"pid":"5c1eae661064a40d47